pageContext.claim: “Yesterday’s Never Trumper witness could find NO Quid Pro Quo in the Transcript of the phone call. There were many people listening to the call. How come they (including the President of Ukraine) found NOTHING wrong with it. Witch Hunt!”
pageContext.analysis: This is false. Lt. Col. Alexander Vindman, the top Ukraine adviser on the National Security Council, testified on Oct. 29: "This was about getting a White House meeting. It was a demand for him to fulfill his—fulfill this particular prerequisite in order to get the meeting." Vindman is a Purple Heart recipient who has denied being a "Never Trumper."
